SAN DIEGO COUNTY DIGEST: SAN DIEGO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A 38-year-old woman was found stabbed to death in her bedroom late Monday, 
authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
The partially clothed body of Elissa Keller was found by her daughter shortly 
before midnight, said San Diego Police Department spokesman Bill Robinson. 
</P>
<P>
The woman lived in the 5200 block of Trojan Avenue in East San Diego, Robinson 
said. No murder weapon was found. 
</P>
