Judge to View Mapplethorpe Photos: A judge said Tuesday he will view the 
controversial Robert Mapplethorpe photo exhibition before it closes at 
Cincinnati's Contemporary Arts Center this weekend. Hamilton County Municipal 
Judge David Albanese, scheduled to be the trial judge in an obscenity case 
concerning the photos, said he will keep the date and time of his visit a 
secret in order to prevent his tour from becoming a media circus. Attorneys for 
both the prosecution and defense had requested that the judge look at the 
