YEMEN -- GOVERNMENT; YEMEN -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- ARAB NATIONS; UNITED STATES 
-- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- YEMEN; NORTH YEMEN -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SOUTH YEMEN; 
MERGERS 
</P>
