<P>
EUROPE -- SECURITY; REUNIFICATION; EAST GERMANY -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST 
GERMANY; NORTH ATLANTIC TREATY ORGANIZATION; WARSAW PACT; EUROPE -- ARMED 
FORCES 
</P>
