died of a single blast to the head. 
</P>
<P>
She was the advertising manager at the Vanguard News newspaper, which serves 
Acton, Agua Dulce and the southern Antelope Valley, a spokeswoman for the paper 
said. The couple's son, Vincent C. Etheredge, is the newspaper's publisher. 
George Etheredge operated an antique mall in Agua Dulce, acquaintances said. 
