<P>
HAMMER, ARMAND; OCCIDENTAL PETROLEUM CORP; INVESTORS; ARMAND HAMMER MUSEUM OF 
ART AND CULTURAL CENTER; CONTRIBUTIONS; ART COLLECTIONS AND COLLECTORS; 
PROPERTY RIGHTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
