<P>
AIRLINE PASSENGERS; TRANSPORTATION SAFETY; BABIES; PUBLIC SAFETY; AIRPLANE 
SAFETY; TRAVEL; GOVERNMENT REGULATION; CHILDREN; NATIONAL TRANSPORTATION SAFETY 
BOARD; CHILD SAFETY; SEATING 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA052390-0129 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 223113 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 23, 1990, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
