<P>
Paramount 7, Magnolia 3 -- Miguel Inzunza's two-run double capped a four-run 
third inning to lead Paramount at Magnolia. 
</P>
<P>
Paramount (16-4), the San Gabriel Valley League champion, scored four runs on 
four hits in the third inning to seal its fourth victory in a row. 
</P>
<P>
